data.eml:eml: A new species of the endemic Australian genus Hyptiogaster Kieffer (Hymenoptera: Gasteruptiidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Parslow, Ben A., Jennings, John T. (2018): A new species of the endemic Australian genus Hyptiogaster Kieffer (Hymenoptera: Gasteruptiidae). Zootaxa 4379 (1): 145-150, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4379.1.11
